summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4133 for the improvement of 10th Avenue West, from West Highland Drive to a connection with the existing pavement on Olympic Way; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 49510, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
